IClassMobile
============

This project is a mobile .NET MAUI adaptation based on ideas and API/WebVPN
workflow references from the open source project:

  iclass_buaa
  https://github.com/zeroduhyy/iclass_buaa

It also references the current BUAA local sign-in and WebVPN workflow used by:

  UBAA
  https://github.com/BUAASubnet/UBAA

The referenced upstream projects are licensed under the MIT License. Their
copyright and permission notices are preserved in LICENSE.

Changes in this repository include a mobile UI, .NET MAUI project structure,
Android packaging, personal-use iClass calendar/sign-in workflow, WebVPN URL
wrapping and login flow adaptation, update checking, and mobile release
packaging.
